node.text: Happy Sunday, friends😊 My days of being able to post pics of my garden goodies are numbered! I'm dreading our first frost but until then, here is a basket showing most of what I grew this year. Peas & beans are done and my guinea pigs ate all of the cilantro & lettuce! If you would like to see pics of my #raisedbedgarden check out my story highlights💚#igrewthis #todaysharvest #gardening #gardeninglife #kellogggarden #sustainablesprout #thehappygardeninglife #gardenersofinstagram #mybackyardgarden #freshfood #freshveggies #michigangardening #michigangarden #gardenlove #organicgardening #raisedbedgardening #backyardgardening

node.text: I feel incredibly fortunate to own/live on land that allows me to forage for edible mushrooms and fresh berries all summer💜 Picking wild blackberries is fun but painful and I have the wounds to back that statement! Ha ha🤪 #wildfood #wildfoodlove #foraging #wildforaging #michiganmushrooms #michiganmushroomhunting #pheasantbackmushroom #dryadssaddle #oystermushrooms #pleurotus #wildblackberries #mushroomseason2021 #forestfinds #nature #ig_naturelovers #fungus #fungi #thisweekoninstagram #upperpeninsulamichigan #michiganoutdoors #upnorthmichigan

It's #tomatotuesday once again and my tomato plants are going crazy! I love getting up in the morning, heading down to the garden and harvesting a whole new batch. I also love #nasturtiums that match! This is what summer is all about😊🍅💚
